ARGUMENT.

As a rule scarcely one or two of the countless friends os this age think on an absent friend. So rare a thing is love. Not only do you think on an absent friend, and not only do you bewail your friend's death, but you give your friend life by your tears. Stmchan, Seton has blessed you, by whose death you shall be styled learned; Strachany you have blessed seton, to whom in death you have granted life.
